pyfaces aims to detect a face from a set applying eigenfaces method.
Fore references http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eigenface

Usage:
    $ python pyfaces.py --help
    Usage: pyfaces.py [options]

    Options:
      -h, --help            show this help message and exit
      -i IMAGE, --image=IMAGE
      -d DIRECTORY, --directory=DIRECTORY
      -f FACES, --faces=FACES
      -t THRESHOLD, --threshold=THRESHOLD
      -s, --show     
